                    <msContents>
                        
                        <summary>A work entitled <title>Gurupūjanavidhi</title>, on <locus>f. 9v</locus> in a hand different from the scribes;
                            cf. <title>Gurupūjā</title> and <title>Gurupūjāvidhi</title> in <abbr>NCC</abbr>, vol. 6, p. 76. Incomplete.
                            On <locus>f. 8</locus> is quoted the <title>Dānamayūkha</title>; presumably this is the so-named section of the
                            <title>Bhagavantabhāskara</title> written by <persName>Nīlakaṇṭha</persName> in about <date>1650</date>.</summary>
                        
                        <textLang mainLang="sa">Sanskrit</textLang>
                        
                        <msItem xml:id="Alpha_2078">
                            <title>Gurupūjanavidhi</title>
                            
                            <incipit> <locus>F. 1v</locus>
                                <!-- Transcript -->
                                śrīmate rāmānujāya namaḥ ||
                                ācinoti ca śāstrārthān
                                ācāre sthāpayati api |
                                svayam ācarate yas tu
                                ācāryaḥ so (')bhidhīyate ||1||
                            </incipit>
                            
                            <explicit> <locus>F. 9</locus>
                                <!-- Transcript -->
                                ... utthāya svakīyaiḥ saha bhojanaṃ kuryāt || brāhmaṇāṃś ca bhojayet | iti
                            </explicit>
                            
                        </msItem>
                        
